stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> queued
  queued --> preflight: promotion.run accepted
  preflight --> blocked: dirty tree, stale branch, invalid target, or missing config
  preflight --> validation: gates pass
  validation --> blocked: tests or SDD doctor fail
  validation --> release_preparation: validation passes
  release_preparation --> blocked: missing tag, secrets, URLs, or updater config
  release_preparation --> waiting_user_approval: release plan ready
  waiting_user_approval --> blocked: approval denied or expired
  waiting_user_approval --> drain_prod: user approves
  drain_prod --> blocked: active PROD jobs do not drain
  drain_prod --> deploy_backend: safe to restart
  deploy_backend --> failed: backend deploy or restart fails
  deploy_backend --> release_prod_app: backend healthy
  release_prod_app --> failed: PROD APK release fails
  release_prod_app --> release_dev_app: PROD app release recorded
  release_dev_app --> failed: DEV APK release fails
  release_dev_app --> post_validation: releases recorded
  post_validation --> failed: health, network, updater, or app identity fails
  post_validation --> notify: all validations pass
  notify --> done: report stored
  failed --> rolled_back: rollback step available and succeeds
  failed --> blocked: rollback unavailable or needs operator action
  blocked --> queued: operator remediates and retries
  done --> [*]
  rolled_back --> [*]

